{"product_id":"idgaf-label","title":"IDGAF LABEL","description":"\n\u003cp\u003e240 GSM.\r\nPUFF PRINT FRONT BACK\r\n100% French Terry Cotton.\r\nGender- Neutral.\r\nBoxy-Fit.\r\nCombed \u0026amp; Bio-washed.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTurn heads without saying a word. This 240 GSM heavyweight T-shirt speaks volumes with its bold front print: “Don’t Smile, Because It Happened Baby”—a savage nod to moving on like a boss. On the back? “Bitche Act Like You Are Not the Inspo”—because you know the truth. Made from premium cotton, it offers a structured fit, rich texture, and durability that matches your energy. Whether you’re flexing solo or throwing shade with style, this tee is the statement your wardrobe needs. Designed for the unapologetic, worn by the unforgettable.\r\n\r\n\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the t-shirt inside out with like colors.\r\nUse cold water to preserve the fabric’s quality.\r\nTumble dry on low heat or air dry to prevent shrinkage and maintain the fabric’s integrity.\r\nStore the t-shirt in a cool, dry place to prevent moisture or mold buildup.\r\n\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eT-shirts with 260 GSM (Grams per Square Meter) for a durable and substantial feel.\r\nOversized fit for comfortable and versatile wear by both men and women.\r\nUnisex article suitable for a wide range of body types and style preferences.\r\nSoft, breathable jersey fabric ensures comfort and airflow.\u003c\/p\u003e\n","brand":"DRIP STUDIOS","offers":[{"title":"M","offer_id":46853862490266,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"L","offer_id":46853862523034,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XS","offer_id":46853862555802,"sku":"oversizedtees-1(-Copy 1)(-Copy 1)","price":1199.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XL","offer_id":4